Kinetic - The Kinetic application framework
================================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

Or, if you don't have Module::Build installed, type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Class::Meta 0.43
   Widget::Meta 0.03
   Exception::Class

